{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-jsx","path":"/pykonik/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"marcingladkowski.com"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"ebd7ab50-6d0b-53f9-b211-dea9f045ec64","excerpt":"Let's kick off meetups in 2026!  That was my first time at a meetup like this - Pykonik. Organized in Kraków by a small group of enthusiasts. There was so much energy and joy. A few interesting topic…","html":"<p>Let's kick off meetups in 2026!</p>\n<p><figure class='gatsby-resp-image-figure' style='margin-bottom: 16px;'>\n    <span class='gatsby-resp-image-wrapper' style='position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 680px; '>\n      <a class='gatsby-resp-image-link' href='/static/226e3ee510917d31e9ef572740552bc3/81f49/pykonik.jpg' style='display: block' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>\n    <span class='gatsby-resp-image-background-image' style=\"padding-bottom: 75.29411764705883%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class='gatsby-resp-image-image' alt='pykonik' title='' src='/static/226e3ee510917d31e9ef572740552bc3/a22ce/pykonik.jpg' srcset='/static/226e3ee510917d31e9ef572740552bc3/0b705/pykonik.jpg 170w,\n/static/226e3ee510917d31e9ef572740552bc3/31389/pykonik.jpg 340w,\n/static/226e3ee510917d31e9ef572740552bc3/a22ce/pykonik.jpg 680w,\n/static/226e3ee510917d31e9ef572740552bc3/29373/pykonik.jpg 1020w,\n/static/226e3ee510917d31e9ef572740552bc3/232dc/pykonik.jpg 1360w,\n/static/226e3ee510917d31e9ef572740552bc3/81f49/pykonik.jpg 4032w' sizes='(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px' style='width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;' loading='lazy' decoding='async'>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class='gatsby-resp-image-figcaption'>pykonik</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>That was my first time at a meetup like this - Pykonik. Organized in Kraków by a small group of enthusiasts. There was so much energy and joy. A few interesting topics were presented: spawning new threads, local coding agents, and music generation.</p>\n<p>My surprise was that so many people were prepared for lightning talks. I saw 6 or 8 people going to the stage one by one to show off some small personal idea or new insight.</p>\n<p><strong>Meetup website and record <a href=\"https://www.pykonik.org/tech-talks/82/\">Pykonik - Tech Talks #82</a></strong></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Meetup Pykonik Kraków","date":"March 26, 2026","update":"March 26, 2026","tags":["python","meetup"],"series":null},"fields":{"slug":"/pykonik/","readingTime":{"minutes":0.47}}},"seriesList":{"edges":[{"node":{"id":"57f2837d-042f-5460-8bb6-fd4495576bc2","fields":{"slug":"/hello-world/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Hello world"}}},{"node":{"id":"15d38b46-7f4e-5d99-92b1-18b74982f8d2","fields":{"slug":"/warsawjs-desing-patterns/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"WarsawJs 44 Design patterns"}}},{"node":{"id":"e9bb0690-14f3-5e9f-9328-584c9f24e8c1","fields":{"slug":"/about/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"About"}}},{"node":{"id":"4ad66fcd-90b1-5304-a213-1c3fc30b256b","fields":{"slug":"/bash-training/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Bash training"}}},{"node":{"id":"48928a16-f1c5-5d1b-a33d-0f50d18db0ff","fields":{"slug":"/bash-training-2/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Bash training 2"}}},{"node":{"id":"3b607386-b659-5272-8fa3-ffa04fb840cb","fields":{"slug":"/summary-2020-plans-for-2021/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Summary 2020 - plans for 2021"}}},{"node":{"id":"6d347c29-ca14-5af3-9aec-3c7e8d0f7a69","fields":{"slug":"/clean-code-workshop/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Clean Code workshop"}}},{"node":{"id":"ef5db6bd-0695-5ada-978e-1ccfd2017d58","fields":{"slug":"/python-crash-course/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Python Crash Course (2nd Edition)"}}},{"node":{"id":"2644cac0-2d10-5868-a75f-137b451040d4","fields":{"slug":"/simple-object-factory/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Simple test object factory"}}},{"node":{"id":"2